## PART 2: COMPONENT SPECIFICATIONS

### Button Variants

**Primary Button (Main CTA):**
- Background: #32B8C6 (brand teal)
- Text Color: #1A1A1A (dark for contrast)
- Padding: 12px 24px
- Font Weight: 600
- Border Radius: 12px
- Hover State: Background changes to #3DD5E3, slight lift effect (translateY -2px)
- Active State: Background changes to #28A5B1, no lift
- Focus State: Teal outline with 3px glow (rgba(50, 184, 198, 0.15))
- Box Shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) on normal, 0 4px 8px on hover

**Secondary Button (Alternative action):**
- Background: Transparent
- Border: 2px solid rgba(232, 232, 232, 0.12)
- Text Color: #E8E8E8
- Hover State: Border becomes #32B8C6, text becomes #32B8C6, slight background tint rgba(50, 184, 198, 0.08)
- Focus State: Focus ring around button

**Icon Button:**
- Background: #2A2A2A
- Padding: 12px
- Border Radius: 8px
- Hover State: Background becomes #353535
- No text, only icons from Lucide React

**Button Sizes:**
- Small: 4px 12px padding, smaller font
- Normal: 12px 24px padding
- Large: 16px 32px padding, larger font
- Full Width: 100% width

### Card Components

**Product Card:**
- Background: #1E1E1E
- Border: 1px solid rgba(232, 232, 232, 0.12)
- Border Radius: 16px
- Overflow: hidden
- Hover Effect: Border becomes #32B8C6 with glow, card lifts (translateY -4px), shadow increases
- Transition: all 250ms cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1)

**Card Layout:**
- Image section with aspect ratio 4:3
- Wishlist button in top-right corner (heart icon)
- Product name, price, discount badge inside card
- Color swatches for frame colors
- "Try Virtual" button at bottom
- Product metadata (ratings, reviews count)

**Image Hover Effect:**
- Zoom in slightly (scale 1.05) on product card hover
- Smooth transition over 350ms

### Navigation Bar

**Sticky Navigation:**
- Background: #1E1E1E with backdrop blur (12px)
- Border Bottom: 1px solid rgba(232, 232, 232, 0.12)
- Height: 64px (plus menu bar)
- Z-Index: 1020 (sticky layer)
- Position: Sticky to top

**Logo Section:**
- Color: #32B8C6 (brand teal)
- Font Size: 20px
- Font Weight: 700
- Display: Flex with 12px gap

**Search Bar:**
- Width: Flexible, max 600px
- Background: #2A2A2A
- Border: 1px solid rgba(232, 232, 232, 0.12)
- Border Radius: 12px
- Padding: 12px 16px
- Focus State: Border becomes #32B8C6, background becomes #353535
- Placeholder Color: #8A8A8A

**Action Buttons:**
- Cart Icon: Display item count badge (red circle with white number)
- Wishlist Icon: Display count badge
- User Avatar: Circular, 32px size
- Hover Effects: Background changes to #2A2A2A

**Navigation Menu (Secondary):**
- Categories: Eyeglasses, Sunglasses, Computer Glasses, Face Shape Guide, Find Doctor, Deals
- Horizontal scroll on mobile
- Underline animation on hover
- Active state: Underline persists with #32B8C6 color

### Form Components

**Text Input:**
- Background: #2A2A2A
- Border: 1px solid rgba(232, 232, 232, 0.12)
- Border Radius: 12px
- Padding: 16px
- Color: #E8E8E8
