## PART 9: IMPORTANT IMPLEMENTATION NOTES

### Dark Mode Best Practices

- Avoid pure black (#000000) and pure white (#FFFFFF)
- Use gradients sparingly (only for hero sections or major CTAs)
- Ensure sufficient contrast between elements
- Use desaturated colors for less eye strain
- Test colors under different lighting conditions
- Provide light mode alternative (optional)

### Indian Market Specific

- All prices in INR (â‚¹)
- Razorpay for payments (primary choice in India)
- Support for UPI, netbanking, card payments, wallets
- Hindi language toggle (optional future phase)
- Indian phone number format (+91)
- Indian pin code format (6 digits)
- Free delivery messaging (popular in India)
- EMI options (popular for eyewear)
- WhatsApp integration (high adoption in India)
- Popular Indian eyewear brands prominently featured

### Mobile First Design

- Start with mobile layout (320px minimum)
- Test on actual mobile devices
- Touch-friendly buttons (min 44px size)
- Avoid hover-only interactions
- Optimize for slower internet connections
- Minimize data usage (reduce image sizes)
- Consider network conditions (offline support optional)

### Image Optimization

- Use Next.js Image component (automatic optimization)
- Multiple image sizes for responsive design
- WebP format with fallback
- Lazy loading for off-screen images
- Placeholder blur effect for better perceived performance
- Compress images before upload (max 500KB per image)
- Use CDN for fast delivery globally

